242
00:13:55,135 --> 00:13:57,673
<i>I got two. I got two. Pagliacci.</i>

243
00:13:57,846 --> 00:14:00,468
<i>Who needs Pagliacci, huh?
Come on, the great tragic clown.</i>

244
00:14:00,641 --> 00:14:03,761
<i>Come on, check it out. He laughs,
